One Thousand trees selected at random from Barro Colorado Island.

Source: R/data.R

One Thousand, randomly chosen, trees from Barro Colorado Island (from the whole plot). Only included data from census 2005 and census 2010.

vft_random_bci

Format

An object of class tbl_df (inherits from tbl, data.frame) with 2257 rows and 32 columns.

Details

This is a slightly cleaned version from a ViewFullTable table. For a raw .csv version see http://bit.ly/fgeo-opendata-vft-random-bci.

Examples
